# TailwindCSS Patterns

## Common Utility Combinations

### Card Container
```tsx
className="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"
```

### Button Base
```tsx
className="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"
```

### Input Base
```tsx
className="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
```

### Flex Center
```tsx
className="flex items-center justify-center"
```

### Flex Between
```tsx
className="flex items-center justify-between"
```

### Grid Layout
```tsx
className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4"
```

### Container with Max Width
```tsx
className="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl"
```

## Spacing Patterns

### Section Padding
- Small: `py-4` or `py-6`
- Medium: `py-8` or `py-12`
- Large: `py-16` or `py-24`

### Component Spacing
- Tight: `space-y-2` or `gap-2`
- Normal: `space-y-4` or `gap-4`
- Loose: `space-y-6` or `gap-6`

## Color Patterns

### Text Colors
- Primary: `text-gray-900`
- Secondary: `text-gray-600`
- Muted: `text-gray-500`
- Accent: `text-blue-600`
- Error: `text-red-600`
- Success: `text-green-600`

### Background Colors
- White: `bg-white`
- Light: `bg-gray-50` or `bg-gray-100`
- Primary: `bg-blue-600`
- Hover: `hover:bg-blue-700`

## Responsive Patterns

### Mobile-First Approach
```tsx
// Mobile: single column, Desktop: 3 columns
className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3"
```

### Hide/Show by Breakpoint
```tsx
// Hidden on mobile, visible on desktop
className="hidden md:block"
```

### Text Size Responsive
```tsx
className="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl"
```

## State Patterns

### Hover States
```tsx
className="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
```

### Focus States
```tsx
className="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
```

### Active States
```tsx
className="active:bg-blue-800"
```

### Disabled States
```tsx
className="disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed"
```

## Animation Patterns

### Transition
```tsx
className="transition-all duration-200"
```

### Hover Scale
```tsx
className="hover:scale-105 transition-transform"
```

### Spin Animation
```tsx
className="animate-spin"
```

## Shadow Patterns

- Small: `shadow-sm`
- Medium: `shadow-md` (most common)
- Large: `shadow-lg`
- Extra Large: `shadow-xl`

## Border Radius Patterns

- Small: `rounded` or `rounded-sm`
- Medium: `rounded-lg` (most common)
- Large: `rounded-xl`
- Full: `rounded-full` (for circles/pills)

## Typography Patterns

### Headings
- H1: `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold`
- H2: `text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold`
- H3: `text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold`
- H4: `text-lg font-semibold`

### Body Text
- Default: `text-base text-gray-700`
- Small: `text-sm text-gray-600`
- Large: `text-lg text-gray-800`

## Layout Patterns

### Full Height Container
```tsx
className="min-h-screen"
```

### Centered Content
```tsx
className="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen"
```

### Sticky Header
```tsx
className="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white shadow-md"
```

### Sidebar Layout
```tsx
// Sidebar
className="w-64 fixed left-0 top-0 h-full"
// Main content
className="ml-64"
```
